data.description: This West Columbia home is beautiful and tucked away. It has one story. This three-bedroom, two-bathroom home has beautiful granite countertops, an open floor plan, a screened-in patio, and a lot more! It's only six years old. This cute starter home is just a few minutes from Lexington Medical Center, as well as a lot of restaurants and stores. It's great for people who want to get away from the noise of the city while still being close enough to everything they need in 10 minutes.
